I. Adding the meta-mitwell-bsp layer to your build
=================================================

Assuming this layer exists at the top-level of your
yocto build tree, you can add it to the build system by adding the
location of the meta-mitwell-bsp layer to bblayers.conf, along with any
other layers needed. e.g.:

  BBLAYERS ?= " \
    /path/to/meta \
    /path/to/meta-poky \
    /path/to/meta-yocto-bsp \
    /path/to/meta-mitwell-bsp \

or you can run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-mitwell-bsp' command.


